window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I founded my empire on lies and bloodshed. Thus they are built. Some name me cursed, but I am an immortal emperor. Attend to my tale. If you dare....</p> <p>I was born when the world was a glorious place, but my parents were betrayed and murdered. I was raised by my sister in fear and poverty instead. That was merely the beginning.</p> <p>I lived through untold death and destruction when the old world was shattered, when creations turned against creators and a new evil rose to assert power.</p> <p>I fought back against the new order and broke humankind free from the shackles of terror that enslaved them. I discovered secrets beyond the lore of all other sorcerers, knowledge that ensures my people will not lack a shepherd on their long march through eternity.</p> <p>And yet the ungrateful world forgets.</p> <p>Bites the hand that feeds it.</p> <p>Comes for me with armies.</p> <p>Sharpens the assassin’s blade.</p> <p>Do you think that I, immortal emperor, greatest of all sorcerers, guardian of my people, will not meet you with fire, sorcery, and steel?</p>"; 
